Gender Pay Gap Reporting 2017

Gender pay gap reporting at  
ArcelorMittal Distribution Solutions UK

This report contains ArcelorMittal Distribution 
Solutions UK’s 2017 gender pay gap information, as 
required under The Equality Act 2010 (Gender Pay Gap 
Information) Regulations 2017.
In compliance with this regulation, ArcelorMittal 
Distribution Solutions UK Ltd (AMDS UK) has calculated 
and disclosed the gender pay gap, for all UK permanent 
employees, at AMDS UK.  

AMDS UK is a subsidiary of ArcelorMittal, consisting of 5 
sales and distribution sites and 2 sales offices. It supplies 
a full range of steel products to customers in the UK.  
The results below are specifically for AMDS UK and 
do not relate to the ArcelorMittal group or other 
ArcelorMittal subsidiaries.

